title: DICK DALE - Calling Up Spirits (1996) (192kbs) [King of Surf Gui
description:
Dick Dale - LEGEND!  That&#039;s it then...O.K. Dick has been recording surf guitar epics since Jimi Hendrix was in short trousers. PULP FICTION brought the man, the legend, to every ones attention & this here album is the first newly recorded work since then.  There&#039;s some suprises...Dick, the legend, sings! Dick, the legend, plays trumpet! Dick, the legend, does covers! This is a historic album by a historic performer.  Well O.K. then, a legend.  Released 3/6/96.
